nodes.text: Frorral was a female corporal in the Special Forces of the Alliance to Restore the Republic during the Galactic Civil War against the Galactic Empire. Frorral was recommended by General Crix Madine to be part of the Endor strike team to take out the second Death Star's shield generator on Endor but according to Caluan Ematt Frorral said she had come down with fur rash, resulting in her not making the squad.
